timeline.body:
What do you think about exposing `requestedMetrics` but readonly? e.g.

```java
Set<String> getRequestedMetrics() {
   return Collections.unmodifiableSet(requestedMetrics);
}
```

Then the test can just do:

```java
assertThat(request1.getRequestedMetrics(), equalTo(request2.getRequestedMetrics()));
```

